The backend must be pointed to an existing frontend installation,
along with standard prefix/compiler CMake flags. For example,

$ cmake ${source} \
   -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=${backend_prefix} \
   -DCMAKE_CXX_COMPILER=${cxxcompiler} \
   -DDARMA_ROOT=${frontend_prefix}

where the configuration points to a DARMA frontend installed
at the ${frontend_prefix}

